    "These two categories cover majority of the information about the company's marketing strategies and planning skills to gain profit in the business.",
    "A good marketing strategy is the utmost reason that brings revenue to the company.",
    "A company can strategize its marketing techniques to sell its products and gain profit in several ways.",
    "For example, identifying new customers who might be interested in the product as well as maintaining existing customers in the business by maintaining product quality (Thorleuchter et al. 2012), using social media platforms to market new products, analyzing the product with the correct market sector to gain utmost popularity and customer satisfaction (Azizi et al. 2009) are all important means of marketing strategy.",
